						               													<description>Fates and Favors is a strategic, team-based, track-movement game combined with Greek mythology.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players are Greek heroes invited to Mount Olympus to pay tribute to the gods by building temples in their honor. To win the game, heroes work with their teammate to complete two temples before the other team.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Heroes use the game&amp;rsquo;s dynamic card play to strategically choose actions in response to the evolving gameplay. Fate cards are the primary basis for movement while Favor cards are powerful interventions from the Olympians. While heroes have the means to control their own fate through clever moves and efficient teamwork, a few perfectly timed godly favors can unexpectedly shift the momentum of the competition in the blink of an eye!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Fates and Favors&amp;rsquo; is finely-tuned to provide heroes memorable experiences with epic comebacks, sweet revenge, and high-stakes anticipation as both teams race to complete their temples!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
